{"tid":104496,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【689有份？】肖建華會唔會出賣香港富豪？","createTime":"2017-02-02T07:04:51.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-03T02:55:56.000Z","uid":44358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"7ab090de26375ec58e4239705cdc26c4479d2042","tid":104496,"uid":44358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T07:04:51.000Z","msg":"有「神秘資本大鱷」之稱的明天系掌門人肖建華，多年來與一班香港富豪關係耐人尋味，他在歲晚被挾上大陸，震撼中港政商界，或令這班富豪人人自危。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n話說回來，在那個江澤民掌權的年代，香港又有一班甘願借出名氣參與這個資本遊戲、有錢齊齊搵的本港富豪，口講無據，各位可以追溯幾單大刁，其中最轟動的要數中策（235）擬蛇吞象收購台灣的南山人壽的陣容，竟然與一個於2014年成立、名叫「香港文化產業聯合總會」的組織巧合的相似。<br />\n<br />\n而據《明報》引述這個非牟利團體的財務報表，截至15年底這組織已獲逾7000萬收入。<span style=\"color: red;\">這個組織由肖建華擔任副會長，梁振英擔任榮譽贊助人、理事會會長是林建岳，其他董事包括新世界發展（017）主席鄭家純、信置（083）主席黃志祥、英皇楊受成、星島集團（1105）主席何柱國</span>及內地女明星趙薇等。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56250697&amp;category_guid=7015342&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170202\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56250697%26category_guid%3D7015342%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170202&d=96kHarChHvhp0Q8MKJCyEAtTNu1qqkxUxYmVHECffP4%3D&h=567016fc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56250697%26category_guid%3D7015342%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170202&h=6eeb0cfa\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56250697&amp;category_guid=7015342&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170202</a>"},{"pid":"83fa6695b22757367d2a6fe6106b45efe3bd6a1e","tid":104496,"uid":9104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T07:08:33.000Z","msg":"很大的棋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb2251068eba11510fb72320dd39960249a638d2","tid":104496,"uid":62815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T07:09:56.000Z","msg":"一鑊炒起<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ff6b80c65e2a347580c1